<html>
<head>
  <title>Conti Leaks</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="bootstrap.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="custom.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container top-padding">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-4 bottom-padding">
        <div class="small-break">&nbsp;</div>
        <center><h1>CONTI<br>NEWS</h1></center>
      </div>
      <div class="col-8">
        <div class="rounded-div">
          If you are a client who declined the deal and did not find your data on cartel's website or did not find valuable files, this does not mean that we forgot about you, it only means that data was sold and only therefore it did not publish in free access!
          <div class="big-break">&nbsp;</div>
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-10">
              <input type="text" class="form-control">
            </div>
            <div class="col-2">
              <input type="button" value="Search" class="btn btn-primary">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div><br><br>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-4">
        <div class="rounded-div fixed-height">
          We are looking for a buyer to access the network of <b>{{ organisation }}</b> and sell data from their network. This organisation is the leading provider in their sector.
          <br><br>
          Total leaked size: <b>{{ leaked_size }}</b><br><br>
          First leaked file: <b>{{ leaked_name }}</b>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-4">
        <div class="rounded-div fixed-height">
          We are looking for a buyer to access the network of this organisation and sell data from their network. This organisation is a world leading manufacturer of stainless steel storage and processing vessels, agitators and integrated systems.
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-4">
        <div class="rounded-div fixed-height">
          We are looking for a buyer to access the network of this organisation and sell data from their network. This organisation is a family owned printer company.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
